==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unalloyed
<hw>Un`al*loyed"</hw> <pr>(⟦ucr⟧n`⟦acr⟧l*loid")</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<def>Not alloyed; not reduced by foreign admixture; unmixed;
unqualified; pure; <as>as, <ex>unalloyed</ex> metals; <ex>unalloyed</ex>
happiness</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I enjoyed <qex>unalloyed</qex> satisfaction in his company.</q>
<rj><qau>Mitford.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unalmsed</ent>⟦br⟧
